<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHINA'S LOST GENERATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The article is a bittersweet reminder of what could have been, and what is, in 
China, and of what the Bush administration could have done, but didn't, in the 
United States. 
</P>
<P>
Thanks to you and your colleagues, the world knows there are Americans who 
still remember and support the courage and integrity of the young people of 
China. 
</P>
<P>
THE COZAD FAMILY, Santa Monica 
</P>
</TEXT>
