<P>
To all the people who worked on "Cartoon All-Stars to the Rescue," the 
anti-drug cartoon for children, I would like to say a big thank you! My 
children loved the show and learned a lot. 
</P>
<P>
It's so nice to see everyone pulling together for the children. They are our 
future. Here's to the children, for a bright and drug-free future! 
</P>
<P>
Judy Ingels, Culver City 
</P>
