<P>
Photo, LaToya Watson, 3, left, and her cousin, LaGerald, 4, peer through the 
screen of their home in Panther Burn Plantation, Miss. They live with 16 
relatives in a four-room shanty without plumbing or an outhouse. Associated 
Press 
</P>
