<TEXT>
<P>
Experts, experts and more experts. All under one roof and available all day to 
help answer your real estate questions. That's what The Times' home 
</P>
<P>
buyers fairs are all about. 
</P>
<P>
Come talk with realtors, home builders, lenders, tax and legal experts, 
representatives from HUD, VA, FHA, CHFA, the Department of Real Estate, the IRS 
