<P>
HOME BUYERS FAIR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
With the various mortgage loans, lenders, rates, terms and government programs 
now available, financing can be the most confusing aspect of home buying. 
</P>
<P>
But it's one of the most important, and it's vital that you understand the 
dollars and sense of your home purchase. 
</P>
<P>
For help in sorting out financing options, come talk to experts -- lenders, 
mortgage brokers, state and federal government representatives -- at this 
Saturday's home buyers fair. 
