<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $54 Saturday when his two horses in the 
seventh race of his $9 triple, Swing Shift and T.V. Screen, failed to win. Bob, 
who started the meeting with a mythical $1,000 bankroll, is at $546. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's bet today is a $25 win parlay from A Shade Faster in the fifth to 
Patapsco in the ninth. 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Bankroll: $600 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Loss: $54 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $546 
</P>
</TEXT>
