FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EASTERN EUROPE; VOLUNTEERS; SPEECHES; CITIZENS DEMOCRACY 
CORPS; CULTURAL EXCHANGES; LOANS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN AID -- POLAND; 
