USSR; SELF REPRESENTATION; NATIONALISM; GORBUNOVS, ANATOLIJS; RUUTEL, ARNOLD; 
LANDSBERGIS, VYTAUTAS; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL S; COUNCIL OF BALTIC STATES 
</P>
