</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
First American Financial Corp., the Santa Ana parent company of First American 
Title Insurance Co., reported net income of $852,000 for the first quarter, 
contrasted with a loss of $1.3 million for the first quarter of 1989. Revenue 
declined 1% to $163.6 million. 
</P>
