<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Vestro Foods Inc.: The Newport Beach speciality food company said first-quarter 
net income totaled $66,000, contrasted with a loss of $170,000 for last year's 
first quarter. 
</P>
<P>
The 1990 three-month period included an extraordinary gain of $49,000 from a 
net operating loss carry-forward. Sales rose 52% to $6.7 million from $4.4 
million. The company attributed the sales increase to the acquisition of Little 
Bear Organic Foods Inc. in the fourth quarter of 1989. 
</P>
</TEXT>
